# A list of all packages that I'm using

xclip; copy screenshot images to clipboard
scrot; make screenshots happen
fastfetch; better version of neofetch, showcase in terminal
nvidia-driver; graphic drivers
firmarware-misc-nonfree; complementary to nvidia-driver
picom; compositor, used achieve transparency in windows
alacritty; fast render terminal
slock; lock screen
libnotify-bin; send notifications
xdotool; automatically fill forms, used with keepass
keepass2; passwords and other secrets management;http://ftp.de.debian.org/debian/pool/main/k/keepass2/keepass2_2.57+dfsg-1_all.deb
code; development editor;https://code.visualstudio.com/sha/download?build=stable&os=linux-deb-x64
git; version management
lightdm; display/login manager
linux-headers-$(uname  -r); complementary to nvidia-driver
awesome; window manager
btop; better version of htop, see tasks/processes
xserver-xorg-input-synaptics; control touchpad
rofi; create graphical menus from text.